{"tid":603712,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[又一個華生]祖迪羅正式現身《驚奇隊長》片場","createTime":"2018-03-24T03:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T05:36:08.000Z","uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7ba1b8fac7deae38e26daf7d88d5b36a9a25cd8d","tid":603712,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T03:59:31.000Z","msg":"Marvel電影世界觀百科<br />\n已讚好的專頁 &middot; 2分鐘 &middot; <br />\n <br />\n裘德˙洛（Jude Law）正式現身《驚奇隊長》片場。<br />\n<br />\n幾個月前Variety曾在一篇獨家報導中指出，裘德˙洛將會在這部電影裡飾演華特˙洛森博士（Dr. Walter Lawson），這名角色在電影裡會擁有類似心靈導師的定位，讓布麗˙拉森（Brie Larson）飾演的主角卡蘿˙丹佛斯（Carol Danvers）可以在適應自身超能力的過程中獲得某種指引。<br />\n<br />\n而值得注意的是，在漫畫裡，華特˙洛森其實正是初代「驚奇隊長」馬維爾（Mar-Vell）在地球使用的身份，卡蘿的「驚奇隊長」稱號亦是由此繼承。<br />\n<br />\n當然了，這則消息尚未經過官方的證實，因此目前只能確定裘德˙洛的確參與了《驚奇隊長》的演出，關於其飾演的角色細節仍有待進一步的確認。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/attachments/day_180324/20180324_991136efe05fa0d0474frBgD2YZrApUV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_180324%2F20180324_991136efe05fa0d0474frBgD2YZrApUV.jpg&h=db8523c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他照片請見：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.justjared.com/2018/03/23/brie-larson-runs-to-meet-jude-law-on-captain-marvel-set/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.justjared.com%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2Fbrie-larson-runs-to-meet-jude-law-on-captain-marvel-set%2F&d=h6VOf%2BDcfMswPncNcCHfFfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=09c71d09\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.justjared.com/2018/03/23/brie-larson-runs-to-meet-jude-law-on-captain-marvel-set/</a>"},{"pid":"afa3681b8b8121535077203e122305aa923335a0","tid":603712,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T04:00:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ff781f691a3dab2e26c8ded385836319b65d434","tid":603712,"uid":5014,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T04:01:13.000Z","msg":"經期隊長？"},{"pid":"d7bcfa7705f2790973815f3c755562426a835504","tid":603712,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s